This directory is a catchall to contain various scripts to build and
analyze games using the Python bindings for Gambit.

Strategic (normal-form) games:
------------------------------
minint.py               The minimum unique integer game
randomnfg.py            Construct a strategic game with randomly-generated
                        payoffs
scp.py, acp.py          Cost allocation in congestion games
                        (see Chen, Razzolini, Turocy, _Economic Theory_)


Extensive games:
----------------

torr.py is a generic engine for constructing extensive games.  Sample
applications:

nim.py                  The game of nim
poker.py                A one-card poker game
ttt.py                  Tic-tac-toe
